Description: Remove bloatware from fresh Debian desktop installations
 Debian Desktop Optimizer helps remove unnecessary language packs, fonts,
 input methods, games, dictionaries and optional desktop components from
 a freshly installed Debian system, while preserving the user's chosen
 languages.
 .
 Features:
  * Graphical wizard for first-run setup
  * Command-line interface with rich output
  * Shared backend — no duplicated logic
  * Safe simulation before any changes
  * Rollback/restore support
  * YAML-driven language database
